#Installing

1. Create a Python virtual environment and activate it.

  i. If you do not have virtualenv install it
      pip3 install virtualenv

  ii. Initialise your virtual environment
    virtualenv -p python3 venv
    source venv/bin/activate


2. Install the package and all of its requirements.
    pip install -e .


#Downloading Updated Data

  i. Download dataset from: https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications-data/download-todays-data-geographic-distribution-covid-19-cases-worldwide 
  ii. Copy dataset to data directory.
  iii. Remember to point scripts to latest dataset


#Plotting Country Data

  i. Run Script script/plot_data.py using country code.
  
#Plotting All Country Case Data on a Log-Log plot

  i. Run Script script/log_plotting.py.
